# This branch (`release`) is the public showroom for github.com/Hilopio/PRIMO.
# It must contain ONLY documentation. Everything else is ignored so that a
# plain `git add .` can never leak source code, the wheel, or dev leftovers
# into the showroom repo. Development happens on other branches, where these
# files are tracked and therefore unaffected by this ignore list.
/*
!.gitignore
!LICENSE
!NOTICE
!README.md
!THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md
